## ðŸ§ª POST-DEPLOYMENT TESTING

### Critical Tests (Must Pass)

1. **Direct URL Access**
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/`
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/services`
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/blog`
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/blog/1`
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/blog/14`
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/contact`
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/projects`
   - [ ] `https://your-domain.vercel.app/invalid-url` (should show 404 page)

2. **Page Refresh Test**
   - [ ] Navigate to any page
   - [ ] Press F5 to refresh
   - [ ] Page should reload without 404 error

3. **Navigation Test**
   - [ ] Click all navbar links
   - [ ] Test footer links
   - [ ] Use browser back/forward buttons
   - [ ] All should work smoothly

4. **Mobile Responsiveness**
   - [ ] Test on mobile device or DevTools
   - [ ] Check hamburger menu (if applicable)
   - [ ] Verify touch interactions

5. **Performance Test**
   - [ ] Run Lighthouse audit
   - [ ] Check page load speed
   - [ ] Verify images load correctly

